metadata.name: a little difference with online
metadata.description:
number of deaths, online games can be unlimited resurrection, but Blue Star data has a death limit, everyone has three deaths at the beginning.



When you run out of deaths, you're dead.



Of course, IF you have a number of deaths, you can also get a number of deaths, such as the first kill of the BOSS in the wild, the first pass of the replica.



Beyond that, it's all about activities and adventures.
